<i>noun</i>: 안약 [아ː냑], 눈약 [눈냑] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>안약 [아ː냑]</dt><br>
<dd>eyewash; eyewater</dd><br>
<dd>눈병이 났을 때 눈에 넣는 약.</dd><br>
<dd>The medicine for eye diseases.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>눈약 [눈냑]</dt><br>
<dd>eyewash</dd><br>
<dd>눈병을 낫게 하기 위해 쓰는 약.</dd><br>
<dd>Medicine in liquid form applied to the eye to cure an eye disease.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>